mosis and fatal cryptococcosis, especially deadly in immunocompromised individuals. This review provides an overview of bat guano microbiota diversity and the significance of autochthonous and pathogenic taxa for humans and the environment, highlighting better understanding in preventing emerging diseases.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Dimki\u0107, Ivica", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fira, Djordje", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Janakiev, Tamara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kabi\u0107, Jovana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stupar, Milo\u0161", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nenadi\u0107, Marija", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Unkovi\u0107, Nikola", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Grbi\u0107, Milica Ljaljevi\u0107", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/980b9d61bda513dccd1fc3cb7a018d9f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/037818151ecbd5d79793e56588e815cbe638185fa2cd8b4c0843e822b93621b3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/4VT74RZK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/4VT74RZK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/41bbc676e3ba7938051f61403df66448!/b232638-235101", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages"